1. Ona ima *graciozan* hod. (She has a graceful walk.)
2. Poklonio mi se s *gracioznošću*. (He greeted me with grace.)
3. *Graciozno* se nasmiješila kad je vidjela poklon. (She smiled graciously when she saw the gift.)
4. Plesačica se *graciozno* savila unatrag. (The dancer gracefully arched backwards.)
5. *Gracija* je bila omiljena tema u umjetnosti renesanse. (Grace was a favorite subject in Renaissance art.)
6. Molim te, učini to s *gracioznošću*. (Please do it with grace.)
7. *Graciozan* pokret ruke izazvao je divljenje publike. (The graceful movement of the hand elicited admiration from the audience.)
8. Pokreti jogija su *graciozni* i harmonični. (The movements of a yogi are graceful and harmonious.)
9. *Gracije* su bile božice ljepote, šarma i radosti u grčkoj mitologiji. (The Graces were goddesses of beauty, charm, and joy in Greek mythology.)
10. Prekrasna *gracija* stajala je na vrhu kola. (A beautiful grace stood at the top of the carriage.)